WEBVTT

00:01.935 --> 00:03.471
Jonas: PREVIOUSLY
ON THE UNIT...

00:03.504 --> 00:05.706
MAC THINKS YOU'RE HAVING
AN AFFAIR?
YES.

00:05.739 --> 00:06.540
AND ARE YOU?

00:06.574 --> 00:08.176
I NEVER EVEN KISSED
THE MAN, I SWEAR.

00:08.209 --> 00:09.843
YOU CAN STAY HERE
TILL MACK COMES HOME.

00:09.877 --> 00:12.880
THEN YOU'LL TALK TO HIM,
FACE TO FACE.

00:12.913 --> 00:14.982
C.I.A. COULD
USE A MAN INSIDE
THE UNIT.

00:15.015 --> 00:15.883
FORGET IT.

00:15.916 --> 00:17.251
YOU CAN'T JUMP OUT
OF AIRPLANES FOREVER.

00:17.285 --> 00:18.419
I THINK I GOT
A FEW YEARS LEFT.

00:18.452 --> 00:19.753
AS YOU RECALL,
ART SPARE HERE

00:19.787 --> 00:22.223
WANTED TO INDUCT YOU
INTO A LITTLE SECRET
OF THE UNIT.

00:22.256 --> 00:25.059
A MAN HAS TO WALK AWAY
AND CAN'T COME BACK.

00:25.093 --> 00:26.060
HOW'S IT PAID FOR?

00:26.094 --> 00:28.962
A UNIT MEMBER
HAS TO DISAPPEAR.

00:30.731 --> 00:32.966
ONCE IN,
NEVER OUT.

00:34.402 --> 00:35.603
[GUNSHOTS]

00:35.636 --> 00:39.973
CAPTIONING MADE POSSIBLE BY
20th CENTURY FOX AND CBS

00:47.548 --> 00:50.251
[GUNSHOTS CONTINUE]

00:54.422 --> 00:56.590
[BOB GRUNTS]

01:02.496 --> 01:04.332
[GROANING]

01:05.733 --> 01:08.269
UH-OH. HEAD WOUNDS
BLEED A LOT.

01:08.302 --> 01:10.571
YEAH, I'M OK.

01:10.604 --> 01:11.405
HERE YOU GO.

01:11.439 --> 01:13.607
JUST YOUR SCALP.
AAH.

01:13.641 --> 01:14.442
GET UP.

01:14.475 --> 01:16.310
THERE'S NO WAY
OUT OF HERE.

01:16.344 --> 01:17.745
NO?

01:17.778 --> 01:19.079
NOT ALIVE.

01:19.113 --> 01:20.114
YOU'RE BULLETPROOF?

01:20.148 --> 01:22.783
YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT THIS IS!

01:23.317 --> 01:25.819
[WHISTLES]

01:35.296 --> 01:38.399
YOU TAKE ME BACK,
C.I.A.'S GONNA KILL ME.

01:38.432 --> 01:40.000
THEY WILL KILL ME.

01:40.033 --> 01:41.602
PLEASURES OF
A DOUBLE AGENT.

01:41.635 --> 01:43.304
IT'S A LIE.

01:43.337 --> 01:46.307
IT'S A LIE.
[GUNSHOTS]

01:51.779 --> 01:54.282
LANDSLIDE!
LANDSLIDE!

01:54.315 --> 01:55.949
LET'S GET THE HELL
OUT OF HERE.

01:55.983 --> 01:58.486
[GUNSHOTS CONTINUE]

02:03.691 --> 02:06.960
[STARTS ENGINE]

02:09.497 --> 02:12.500
[TIRES SQUEALING]

02:51.672 --> 02:53.974
HOW'S YOUR MAMA,
MISS MOLLY?

02:54.007 --> 02:55.709
SHE'S DOING FINE,
THANKS.

02:55.743 --> 02:57.411
THAT'S A BLESSING.

02:57.445 --> 02:58.746
HOW DID YOU COME
TO KNOW MY MOTHER?

02:58.779 --> 03:01.915
OH, I REMEMBERED HER
FROM, UH, FROM WHEN
SHE VISITED HERE.

03:01.949 --> 03:04.485
MY MOTHER HASN'T BEEN IN
FORT GRIFFITH IN 15 YEARS.

03:04.518 --> 03:05.486
YOU'VE BEEN HERE
THAT LONG?

03:05.519 --> 03:09.923
[CHUCKLES]
NOW YOU'VE GONE
AND CAUGHT ME.

03:11.725 --> 03:12.593
HEY!

03:12.626 --> 03:13.727
WHAT DO YOU KNOW
ABOUT PRISON?

03:13.761 --> 03:15.496
LEAVENWORTH,
'CAUSE THAT'S WHERE
YOUR HUSBAND

03:15.529 --> 03:17.598
AND HIS BUDS ARE ABOUT
TO SHUFFLE OFF TO.

03:17.631 --> 03:18.932
WHAT IS IT
THAT YOU WANT?

03:18.966 --> 03:20.067
TO EDUCATE YOU.

03:20.100 --> 03:21.101
YOUR JONAS HAS
DONE SOME THINGS

03:21.134 --> 03:23.937
THAT'S IN
HIS BEST INTEREST
WHEN HE COMES HOME,

03:23.971 --> 03:24.938
YOU TELL HIM
IT'S RIGHT

03:24.972 --> 03:26.240
HE COMES FORWARD
AND CONFESSES.

03:26.274 --> 03:28.576
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

03:28.609 --> 03:30.478
YOU'RE ABOUT TO.

03:46.460 --> 03:48.662
MOMMY, MOMMY!

03:51.131 --> 03:53.301
STOP!

03:56.304 --> 03:59.106
BABY, YOU HAVE GOT
TO PAY ATTENTION!

03:59.139 --> 04:01.409
I WAS JUST TRYING
TO HELP.

04:01.442 --> 04:03.811
[SIGHS]

04:04.812 --> 04:08.215
UGH, THEY DRIVE LIKE CRAZY
THROUGH HERE.

04:08.248 --> 04:09.049
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

04:09.082 --> 04:10.784
YEAH. JUST WISH
WE COULD HAVE GOTTEN

04:10.818 --> 04:12.653
THAT MANIAC'S
LICENSE NUMBER.

04:12.686 --> 04:13.787
YOU'RE LIKE MY DADDY.

04:13.821 --> 04:16.957
IS THAT RIGHT? WELL, I'M SURE
THAT'S QUITE A COMPLIMENT.

04:16.990 --> 04:18.125
HE'S BRAVE, TOO.

04:18.158 --> 04:20.160
WELL, I KNOW HE IS,
SABRINA.

04:20.193 --> 04:23.096
HOW DO YOU KNOW
MY DAUGHTER'S NAME?

04:23.130 --> 04:24.398
[SIGHS]

04:24.432 --> 04:25.333
I WANT TO, UH,

04:25.366 --> 04:26.767
I WANT TO HELP YOUR HUSBAND,
MRS. BROWN.

04:26.800 --> 04:28.902
ACTUALLY, I WANT TO HELP
YOUR WHOLE FAMILY.

04:28.936 --> 04:31.271
IF YOU CALL THAT NUMBER
WHEN YOU GET HOME,

04:31.305 --> 04:33.307
THEY WILL VERIFY
THAT I AM WHAT I SAY I AM.

04:33.341 --> 04:36.977
IF YOU DOUBT THE NUMBER,
THEN YOU CAN GET IT
THROUGH THE YELLOW PAGES,

04:37.010 --> 04:38.979
ASK FOR C.I.A.
ASK TO BE PUT THROUGH

04:39.012 --> 04:41.114
TO THE C.I.A.
MAIN SWITCHBOARD,

04:41.148 --> 04:42.783
TELL THEM AGENT KATZ.

04:42.816 --> 04:44.184
WHAT IS THIS?

04:44.217 --> 04:45.118
WHEN YOU'VE MADE THE CALL

04:45.152 --> 04:46.454
I'LL, UH, COME TO YOUR HOUSE
AND EXPLAIN IT.

04:46.487 --> 04:49.390
GOOD-BYE, MRS. BROWN.
IT'S ABOUT YOUR HUSBAND.

04:50.324 --> 04:51.992
BYE.

04:53.226 --> 04:54.962
RENEGADE AGENT.

04:54.995 --> 04:56.930
FEDERAL MARSHALL
TAKES HIM INTO CUSTODY,

04:56.964 --> 04:59.132
STARTS CRYING.

04:59.166 --> 05:00.167
YEP.

05:00.200 --> 05:02.636
LAST ONE TO WRAP UP
BUYS THE BEER?

05:02.670 --> 05:04.137
[CHUCKLES]

05:04.171 --> 05:06.139
YOU MEN...

05:06.173 --> 05:07.541
DROP YOUR BAGS
AND TAKE 2 STEPS BACK.

05:07.575 --> 05:08.976
THIS IS
A RESTRICTED AREA.

05:09.009 --> 05:11.512
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU,
AND WHAT DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE DOING?

05:11.545 --> 05:13.981
I SAID DROP THE BAGS
AND TAKE 2 STEPS BACK.

05:14.014 --> 05:15.683
I'M NOT GONNA
SAY IT AGAIN.

05:15.716 --> 05:16.717
DOES YOUR MAMA
KNOW YOU'RE OUT?

05:16.750 --> 05:18.285
YOU SHOULD TAKE
YOUR HANDS OFF
YOUR WEAPON

05:18.318 --> 05:19.387
UNLESS YOU'RE READY
TO USE IT.

05:19.420 --> 05:20.421
ALL RIGHT,
EVERYBODY STOP.

05:20.454 --> 05:22.490
EVERYONE, TAKE YOUR HANDS
AWAY FROM YOUR WEAPONS.

05:22.523 --> 05:25.826
SERGEANT STRICKLAND,
I AM SERGEANT MAJOR BLANE.

05:25.859 --> 05:26.760
THIS IS MY COMPOUND.

05:26.794 --> 05:29.062
YOU WANT TO TELL ME
WHAT THIS IS ALL ABOUT?

05:29.096 --> 05:30.364
MY ORDERS STATE--
SERGEANT STRICKLAND,

05:30.398 --> 05:32.933
YOU MAY RETURN
TO YOUR PATROL.

05:34.067 --> 05:37.505
YES, SIR.
LET'S GO.

05:38.171 --> 05:43.411
COLONEL BAZEMORE,
30 MINUTES, I'LL MEET YOU
AT YOUR OFFICE.

05:45.379 --> 05:47.681
SERGEANT MAJOR...

05:47.715 --> 05:48.782
THIS ENTIRE ORGANIZATION

05:48.816 --> 05:51.652
IS ON STAND-DOWN
PENDING AN ARTICLE 32
INVESTIGATION

05:51.685 --> 05:53.987
FOR MASSIVE
CRIMINAL ACTION
AND WAR CRIMES

05:54.021 --> 05:55.589
BY MEMBERS
OF THIS COMMAND.

05:55.623 --> 05:57.257
SIR, THAT'S--
THANK YOU, SERGEANT.

05:57.290 --> 06:00.327
AND IT SEEMS THAT
THIS TEAM, YOUR TEAM,
SERGEANT MAJOR,

06:00.360 --> 06:03.063
ARE CENTRAL
TO EVERY ASPECT
OF THOSE ACTIVITIES.

06:03.096 --> 06:04.565
COLONEL,
I'M SURE THERE'S--

06:04.598 --> 06:06.734
IN FACT,
AT THE PRESENT TIME,

06:06.767 --> 06:08.602
YOUR MEN ARE
THE SOLE SUBJECTS

06:08.636 --> 06:12.506
OF THESE POTENTIAL
CRIMINAL CHARGES.

06:12.540 --> 06:13.741
THEREFORE,

06:13.774 --> 06:16.009
PENDING FURTHER
NOTIFICATION,

06:16.043 --> 06:17.010
YOU WILL
HOLD YOURSELVES READY

06:17.044 --> 06:19.346
FOR INTERVIEW
BY INVESTIGATORS
FROM THE C.I.D.

06:19.379 --> 06:20.514
AND I WARN YOU NOW,

06:20.548 --> 06:22.916
THAT IF YOU SPEAK
ABOUT THIS MATTER
AMONGST YOURSELVES,

06:22.950 --> 06:26.520
UNDER LAW, SUCH ACTION
IS CONSIDERED CONSPIRACY.

06:26.554 --> 06:31.959
AND UNDER MILITARY LAW,
CONSPIRACY AGAINST COMMAND
CONSTITUTES MUTINY.

06:31.992 --> 06:33.293
AND, MEN, KNOW YOU WELL

06:33.326 --> 06:38.265
THAT I WILL NOT HESITATE
TO BRING THOSE CHARGES
AGAINST YOU MYSELF.

06:38.298 --> 06:39.800
THIS TEAM,

06:39.833 --> 06:43.103
YOU FIVE MEN,
BY YOUR ACTIONS,

06:43.136 --> 06:47.608
MAY HAVE DESTROYED A UNIT
30 YEARS IN THE MAKING.

06:47.641 --> 06:51.211
NOW, YOU WILL WALK AWAY
AND YOU WILL LEAVE
THIS COMPOUND,

06:51.244 --> 06:53.881
AND YOU WILL WALK AWAY
IN 5 DIFFERENT DIRECTIONS.

06:53.914 --> 06:58.652
AND YOU WILL HAVE NO
FURTHER COMMUNICATIONS
WITH EACH OTHER.

06:59.920 --> 07:02.155
YOU'RE DISMISSED.

