07:21.809 --> 07:22.776
* HERE WE GO
* HERE WE GO

07:22.810 --> 07:24.111
* ON THE ROAD
* ON THE ROAD

07:24.144 --> 07:25.445
* TWENTY-SEVEN
* TWENTY-SEVEN

07:25.479 --> 07:26.446
* FIRED UP
* FIRED UP

07:26.480 --> 07:27.515
* FIRED UP
* FIRED UP

07:27.548 --> 07:28.649
* FIRED UP
* FIRED UP

07:28.682 --> 07:30.117
* TWENTY-SEVEN
* TWENTY-SEVEN

07:30.150 --> 07:32.620
* FIRED UP
* FIRED UP

07:33.453 --> 07:34.988
[GUNSHOT]

07:38.859 --> 07:40.761
COLONEL,
THAT WAS SOME SHOW.

07:40.794 --> 07:41.995
YOU WANT TO TELL ME
WHO'S BEHIND
THE CURTAIN?

07:42.029 --> 07:44.197
I GOT HIT WITH IT
FIRST THING THIS MORNING.

07:44.231 --> 07:46.433
ALL OPERATIONS CEASE,
UNIT CLOSE DOWN.

07:46.466 --> 07:48.969
SENIOR TEAM LEADER
AND HIS MEN UNDER
INVESTIGATION,

07:49.002 --> 07:50.337
BURN BEFORE READING.

07:50.370 --> 07:51.639
THAT BAZEMORE CHARACTER?

07:51.672 --> 07:53.040
WASHINGTON HATCHET MAN,
BEARER OF BAD NEWS.

07:53.073 --> 07:55.976
HE BROUGHT THE ORDERS.
HE'S OVERSEEING THE SHUTDOWN.

07:56.009 --> 07:58.345
WHAT'S THIS ALL ABOUT?

07:59.813 --> 08:00.781
I DON'T REALLY KNOW,

08:00.814 --> 08:03.383
BUT I DO KNOW THAT
WE'RE PERSONA NON GRATA.

08:03.416 --> 08:06.186
NOBODY'S TAKING MY CALLS
IN WASHINGTON D.C.,

08:06.219 --> 08:07.788
NOBODY RETURNS THEM.

08:07.821 --> 08:10.457
ALL INFO COMES THROUGH
BAZEMORE.

08:10.490 --> 08:13.226
COLONEL, DO YOU BELIEVE
FOR ONE SECOND THAT I

08:13.260 --> 08:15.228
OR MY MEN ARE GUILTY
OF SOME CRIME?

08:15.262 --> 08:16.897
I DO BELIEVE
THAT WE'RE IN
THE DEEP BATTER,

08:16.930 --> 08:18.131
AND SOMEBODY
WANTS US THERE.

08:18.165 --> 08:20.668
I DON'T KNOW YET WHO,
AND I DON'T KNOW WHY.

08:20.701 --> 08:24.071
I BELIEVE
THAT THEY CAN
BRING US ALL DOWN.

08:24.104 --> 08:24.972
THE MEN, YOU AND ME,

08:25.005 --> 08:27.174
EVERYTHING
THAT WE'VE CREATED
IS AT RISK.

08:27.207 --> 08:29.142
I'M AT A LOSS.

08:29.176 --> 08:30.544
I'LL LET YOU
AS BEST I CAN

08:30.578 --> 08:31.745
WHAT I KNOW
WHEN I KNOW IT.

08:31.779 --> 08:33.413
AND I'LL TRY
TO GIVE YOU AS MUCH
WARNING AS I CAN,

08:33.446 --> 08:36.316
BECAUSE WHEN THE ARMY
BRINGS ITS FULL WEIGHT
TO BEAR AGAINST YOU,

08:36.349 --> 08:39.519
IT'S GONNA BE COMING
WITH A BIG CRASH.

08:40.220 --> 08:42.790
[WHISPERS]
We'll see you at 6:00.

08:48.729 --> 08:50.230
Jonas: IT'S WHAT
I HAVE TO ASK OF YOU NOW.

08:50.263 --> 08:53.100
NO GROCERY STORE,
EMAILS, PHONE CALLS,
MESSAGES,

08:53.133 --> 08:55.936
PICKING UP MAIL.
GARBAGE?

08:55.969 --> 08:58.238
WE HAVE TO LIVE
OUR LIVES.

08:58.271 --> 08:59.372
WELL,
DIFFERENT LIVES, NOW.

08:59.406 --> 09:01.742
ASSUME YOU'RE BEING
FOLLOWED, PHONES ARE TAPPED,

09:01.775 --> 09:04.745
EYES AND EARS ARE ON US
ALL THE TIME.

09:04.778 --> 09:07.114
YOU'VE GIVEN YEARS
OF SERVICE.

09:07.147 --> 09:09.216
YEAH, WELL...

09:10.217 --> 09:13.220
I'M THE RED-HEADED
STEPCHILD NOW.

09:14.655 --> 09:15.789
WHY?

09:15.823 --> 09:16.924
WHEN THE TORTURER COMES,

09:16.957 --> 09:20.060
THE LAST THING
IN THE WORLD YOU WANT
TO BE IS INNOCENT,

09:20.093 --> 09:22.930
BECAUSE YOU GOT NOTHING
TO CONFESS.

09:22.963 --> 09:23.997
AND KNOW, BABY,

09:24.031 --> 09:28.636
ANYTHING THEY ACCUSE US OF
BEYOND WHAT WE HAD TO DO,

09:28.669 --> 09:31.571
OR WHAT WE WERE
CHARGED TO DO...

09:32.472 --> 09:35.308
WE DID NOT DO.

09:35.342 --> 09:36.309
IN CASE.

09:36.343 --> 09:37.811
YOU THINK I NEED THAT?

09:37.845 --> 09:40.781
I SINCERELY HOPE NOT.

09:40.814 --> 09:44.484
A GOOD SOLDIER
ALWAYS HAS PLAN "B."

09:46.286 --> 09:48.922
BECAUSE TODAY...

09:48.956 --> 09:51.959
IS THAT RAINY DAY.

09:56.263 --> 09:57.631
WHO ARE YOU?

09:57.665 --> 09:59.599
I'M FROM
THE AGENCY, BOB.

09:59.633 --> 10:01.268
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
IN MY HOUSE?

10:01.301 --> 10:02.770
HE SAYS THE TEAM'S
GOING TO PRISON.

10:02.803 --> 10:04.137
BUT IT DOESN'T HAVE
TO GO THAT WAY.

10:04.171 --> 10:07.074
THE CHARGES
COULD FOCUS SOLELY
ON THE MISDEEDS

10:07.107 --> 10:08.408
COMMITTED BEFORE
YOU JOINED THE UNIT.

10:08.441 --> 10:09.910
WHO THE HELL
DO YOU THINK YOU ARE?

10:09.943 --> 10:12.612
[SCOFFS] I'M THE MAN
WHO'S BRINGING YOU
A CHOICE.

10:12.646 --> 10:13.747
I THINK
I'M YOUR FRIEND.

10:13.781 --> 10:14.982
YOUR WORM YOUR WAY
INTO MY HOUSE,

10:15.015 --> 10:16.750
SCARE MY WIFE
WITH GHOST STORIES,

10:16.784 --> 10:17.718
AND YOU'RE MY FRIEND?

10:17.751 --> 10:19.286
BOB, YOU'VE GOT
A BIG DECISION
TO MAKE HERE.

10:19.319 --> 10:21.121
YOUR WIFE PLAYS
A HUGE PART IN THAT.

10:21.154 --> 10:23.090
I THINK--
GET THE HELL
OUT MY HOUSE!

10:23.123 --> 10:25.726
BOB, HE WANTS--
GET OUT NOW!

10:28.495 --> 10:31.164
DON'T LET A MISPLACED
SENSE OF LOYALTY
BEND YOUR THINKING.

10:31.198 --> 10:32.465
A MISPLACED
SENSE OF LOYALTY?

10:32.499 --> 10:35.302
THE REST OF YOUR FRIENDS
ARE GONNA GO TO JAIL.
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

10:35.335 --> 10:37.637
YOU'VE GOTTA
SEPARATE YOURSELF
FROM THAT.

10:37.671 --> 10:38.505
WE NEED YOU.

10:38.538 --> 10:41.508
JUST GET OUT
OF MY HOUSE,
ALL RIGHT?

10:42.042 --> 10:45.578
COMPANY NEEDS
MEN LIKE YOU.

10:47.480 --> 10:49.116
[DOOR CLOSES]

10:49.149 --> 10:51.218
BOB, I'M SCARED.

10:51.251 --> 10:54.154
[SIGHS]

11:52.946 --> 11:54.882
TIFFY...

12:35.322 --> 12:39.159
TARGET HAS
SWITCHED VEHICLES.

12:44.197 --> 12:46.766
[BEEPING]

12:48.635 --> 12:51.004
BACK TRAIL'S CLEAR.
MONITORS ARE SET.

12:51.038 --> 12:53.606
IF ANYBODY APPROACHES,
WE'LL HAVE PLENTY
OF WARNING.

12:53.640 --> 12:54.808
WHERE'S GREG?

12:54.842 --> 12:55.876
WE MIGHT HAVE HAD A TAIL.

12:55.909 --> 12:57.811
CARLITO COULDN'T SHAKE HIM.
WOULDN'T MEET HIM HERE.

12:57.845 --> 12:59.312
I'LL FILL HIM IN LATER.

12:59.346 --> 13:00.680
WELL, THEN,
LET'S PROCEED.

13:00.713 --> 13:02.615
WE MAY NOT HAVE
MUCH TIME.

13:02.649 --> 13:03.951
SO WHAT TO DO?

13:03.984 --> 13:06.820
WHAT THE HELL
IS THIS ALL ABOUT,
ANYWAY? IRAN?

13:06.854 --> 13:08.288
MISSING DIAMONDS,
OUR MISSION
IN HONDURAS?

13:08.321 --> 13:09.990
IT COULD BE ANY ONE
OF A DOZEN THINGS.

13:10.023 --> 13:11.291
THOSE WERE
LEGITIMATE MISSIONS.

13:11.324 --> 13:12.459
WE WERE
FOLLOWING ORDERS.

13:12.492 --> 13:13.961
WHAT ORDERS
ARE THOSE?

13:13.994 --> 13:15.462
YOU HAVE COPIES
OF THOSE ORDERS?

13:15.495 --> 13:16.796
THERE ARE NO
WRITTEN ORDERS.

13:16.830 --> 13:18.631
WE'RE AT WAR.
HAS THE WHOLE WORLD
FORGOTTEN THAT?

13:18.665 --> 13:20.800
WHY WOULD ANYBODY
WANT TO SHUT US DOWN?

13:20.834 --> 13:21.969
WELL, THAT'S
THE QUESTION.

13:22.002 --> 13:23.937
GENTLEMEN, IN THE ARMY,
TO BE CHARGED IS TO BE
CONVICTED.

13:23.971 --> 13:28.041
OH, YES, AND
THEY WILL MANUFACTURE
ALL THE PROOF THEY NEED.

13:28.075 --> 13:29.442
BUT THERE ARE RECORDS.

13:29.476 --> 13:31.044
MEMORANDUMS OF RECORD.

13:31.078 --> 13:32.846
TRANSCRIPTS OF
THE VERBAL MISSION ORDER

13:32.880 --> 13:35.615
COME DOWN FROM HEADQUARTERS
BLACK OPS.

13:35.648 --> 13:36.683
I'VE NEVER HEARD
OF THAT.

13:36.716 --> 13:37.684
FIRST COMMANDER
COLONEL BARTLETT

13:37.717 --> 13:38.986
INSTITUTED IT BACK
IN THE SEVENTIES.

13:39.019 --> 13:41.288
HE WAS AFRAID SOMEDAY
SOMETHING LIKE THIS
WOULD HAPPEN,

13:41.321 --> 13:43.790
HE'D GET LEFT
TWISTIN' IN THE WIND.

13:43.823 --> 13:44.992
AND SO?

13:45.025 --> 13:46.026
HE KEPT A LOG

13:46.059 --> 13:47.961
OF EVERY CONVERSATION
WITH H.Q.

13:47.995 --> 13:51.298
EVERY COMMANDER SINCE
HAS DONE THE SAME.

13:51.331 --> 13:52.900
IS THAT SO?

13:52.933 --> 13:54.034
HAND-WRITTEN NOTES?

13:54.067 --> 13:56.536
UNDER MILITARY LAW,
SUCH A RECORD
STANDS AS EVIDENCE.

13:56.569 --> 13:57.637
YEAH, IF IT EXISTS.

13:57.670 --> 14:01.708
BUT WHERE IS IT?
THE INTEL SHOP?
THE SKIFF?

14:01.741 --> 14:02.709
NO. TOO MANY EYES.

14:02.742 --> 14:05.478
IT'S IN A SAFE
IN THE COMMANDER'S OFFICE.

14:05.512 --> 14:07.647
I'VE BEEN ALL OVER
RYAN'S OFFICE.

14:07.680 --> 14:08.848
I'VE NEVER SEEN A SAFE.

14:08.882 --> 14:10.918
IT'S BEHIND A PLAQUE
ON THE WALL BESIDE
THE OLD MAN'S DESK.

14:10.951 --> 14:13.353
WE PLUGGED IT IN
WHEN WE REBUILT
THE BUILDING.

14:13.386 --> 14:17.624
I GUESS I'M THE ONLY ONE
GOES BACK THAT FAR.

14:22.362 --> 14:23.396
MISS MOLLY ANNE?

14:23.430 --> 14:26.399
YOU KNOW, I CAN'T STAND
THE THOUGHT OF
A FREE RIDE,

14:26.433 --> 14:28.768
SO I DECIDED TO PAY
SOME OF THE TOLL.

14:28.801 --> 14:31.838
I DROPPED THE GIRLS OFF
AT THAT BIRTHDAY PARTY

14:31.871 --> 14:33.840
BONNIE'S HAVING
FOR ANDREW.

14:33.873 --> 14:36.076
YOU MIGHT WANT
TO GO GET 'EM.

14:36.109 --> 14:37.844
NO, I JUST DROPPED
THEM OFF.

14:37.877 --> 14:39.512
THERE'S TROUBLE.

14:39.546 --> 14:42.582
NO, IT'S NOT MACK.
HE'S NOT HURT.

14:42.615 --> 14:43.850
I THOUGHT--
I KNOW.

14:43.883 --> 14:44.851
THIS IS A DIFFERENT
PROBLEM,

14:44.884 --> 14:46.920
AND IT'S
A BIGGER ONE THAN
THE TROUBLES WITH--

14:46.954 --> 14:47.921
DOES MACK KNOW
WHERE WILSON IS?

14:47.955 --> 14:50.023
I NEED YOUR ATTENTION.
IS HE TRYING TO FIND HIM?

14:50.057 --> 14:51.458
PUT THAT ASIDE
AND LISTEN TO ME.

14:51.491 --> 14:52.459
I DON'T--
LISTEN TO ME.

14:52.492 --> 14:55.428
PUT YOUR AND
MACK'S TROUBLES
INTO YOUR POCKET,

14:55.462 --> 14:57.430
AND BELLY UP
TO THE BAR.

14:57.464 --> 14:59.732
AND YOU AIN'T
GONNA LIKE IT.

14:59.766 --> 15:02.135
[SIGHS]

15:02.169 --> 15:04.304
TELL ME.

15:10.077 --> 15:11.744
NICE DAY!

15:11.778 --> 15:13.646
[CAR DOOR SLAMS]
DO I KNOW YOU?

15:13.680 --> 15:15.748
I'M AN INTERESTED PARTY.

15:15.782 --> 15:17.117
IS THAT RIGHT?

15:17.150 --> 15:18.251
HOW'D YOU GET ON BASE?

15:18.285 --> 15:21.421
A MAN COULD DRIVE,
HE COULD WALK.

15:21.454 --> 15:23.723
LET'S SEE SOME I.D.,
FUNNY MAN.

15:23.756 --> 15:26.326
NOW, SEE, THE THING IS,
SERGEANT MAJOR BLANE,

15:26.359 --> 15:28.828
I DON'T NEED ANY I.D.

15:29.429 --> 15:31.464
IF THAT'S
YOUR POSITION...

15:31.498 --> 15:32.799
[GRUNTS]

15:32.832 --> 15:35.802
6 POUNDS OF PRESSURE,
I'M THROUGH YOUR SKIN
INTO YOUR BLACK HEART.

15:35.835 --> 15:38.138
NOW WHO'S BEHIND THIS?

15:38.171 --> 15:38.972
GOD!

15:39.006 --> 15:41.708
JONAS,
THAT'S THE GUY.

15:43.443 --> 15:46.179
YOU THREATENED
MY WIFE?

15:46.213 --> 15:47.847
[GRUNTS]

15:48.348 --> 15:51.418
YOU GOT A QUESTION,
YOU DO NOT ASK MY WIFE.

15:51.451 --> 15:54.121
YOU MAKE A POLITE
INQUIRY OF ME.

15:54.154 --> 15:56.256
YOU'VE GOT 10 SECONDS.

15:56.289 --> 15:58.925
[GROANS]

15:58.958 --> 15:59.926
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

15:59.959 --> 16:02.629
I'M RESTRICTED
TO THE BASE,
NOT MY HOUSE.

16:02.662 --> 16:03.596
WHERE'S THE REST
OF YOUR TEAM?

16:03.630 --> 16:05.132
GOT STRICT ORDERS
NOT TO BE WITH THEM,

16:05.165 --> 16:06.599
SO I COULDN'T TELL YA.

16:06.633 --> 16:08.301
TICK-TOCK, TIME'S UP.

16:08.335 --> 16:09.536
[GRUNTS]

16:09.569 --> 16:11.338
I ONLY ANSWER
TO 2 THINGS, FOOL--

16:11.371 --> 16:13.106
MY CONSCIENCE
AND THE ARMY.

16:13.140 --> 16:15.108
AND MY CONSCIENCE SAYS
YOU AND YOUR POSSE

16:15.142 --> 16:18.478
ARE BARKING UP
THE WRONG MILITARY MAN.

16:19.246 --> 16:21.448
AND IF YOU EVER SPEAK
TO MY WIFE AGAIN,

16:21.481 --> 16:25.818
BUY A BUGLE,
AND FIND A GUY
WHO CAN PLAY TAPS.

16:26.719 --> 16:29.256
[GASPING]

16:38.765 --> 16:40.733
[DOOR OPENS]

16:40.767 --> 16:42.001
YOU AIN'T
TAKING MY KIDS.

16:42.035 --> 16:43.236
WE SUPPOSED TO LEAVE
WITHOUT THEM?

16:43.270 --> 16:44.671
YOU GOIN' TO BE
WITH YOUR BOYFRIEND?

16:44.704 --> 16:46.139
THIS WILSON FELLA,
YOU CAN GO

16:46.173 --> 16:47.840
WITHOUT THE KIDS,
WITHOUT YOUR CLOTHES.

16:47.874 --> 16:49.509
MOLLY TOLD ME
WHAT'S GOING ON
WITH THE UNIT.

16:49.542 --> 16:51.811
I THOUGHT WE WERE GONNA
HAVE TO GET OUT OF HERE.

16:51.844 --> 16:53.680
IS THAT
WHAT YOU THOUGHT?

16:53.713 --> 16:57.584
I WAS PACKING THE GIRLS
AND US TO LEAVE!

16:57.617 --> 16:59.386
AND GO TO HIM!

16:59.419 --> 17:01.421
DON'T LIE TO ME!

17:01.454 --> 17:04.924
YOU'RE GONNA DIVORCE A MAN,
YOU TELL HIM!

17:04.957 --> 17:06.426
IS THIS WHERE
YOU DID IT?

17:06.459 --> 17:08.328
OR DID HE TAKE YOU
TO HIS PLACE?

17:08.361 --> 17:09.596
THIS WASN'T ABOUT WILSON!

17:09.629 --> 17:11.431
OUR DIVORCE ISN'T ABOUT
YOUR BOYFRIEND?

17:11.464 --> 17:12.565
IT'S ABOUT US!

17:12.599 --> 17:13.866
YOU MADE IT ABOUT HIM
WHEN YOU SLEPT WITH HIM!

17:13.900 --> 17:17.637
LOOK AT THE DATE, YOU BULLY!
I NEVER FILED IT!

17:18.105 --> 17:19.106
A YEAR AGO?

17:19.139 --> 17:21.174
YOU WERE WITH HIM
A YEAR AGO?!

17:21.208 --> 17:23.210
I NEVER SLEPT WITH WILSON!
I SAW YOU WITH HIM!

17:23.243 --> 17:25.678
I DIDN'T SLEEP WITH HIM!

17:25.712 --> 17:26.679
WHO WAS IT?

17:26.713 --> 17:28.848
DID YOU HAVE A GO
WITH ANYONE
TO HUMILIATE ME?

17:28.881 --> 17:30.950
WHO WAS IT, TIFFY?
WAS IT ONE OF MY BUDDIES?

17:30.983 --> 17:32.952
WAS IT A STRANGER,
SOMEBODY YOU PICKED UP?

17:32.985 --> 17:34.721
YOU SELF-IMPORTANT,
SELF-RIGHTEOUS PUNK!

17:34.754 --> 17:36.623
YOU WANT TO KNOW
WHAT'S GOING ON WITH--

17:36.656 --> 17:37.590
I ALREADY KNOW!

17:37.624 --> 17:39.226
HE TALKS TO ME
AND I LIKE IT!

17:39.259 --> 17:40.927
HE LISTENS TO ME
AND I LIKE THAT.

17:40.960 --> 17:42.929
HE CONFIDES IN ME,
AND I KNOW,
END OF THE DAY,

17:42.962 --> 17:46.466
I WON'T GET A CALL
HE'S DEAD!

17:46.499 --> 17:49.302
DID I SLEEP WITH HIM? NO.
DID I WANT TO?

17:49.336 --> 17:51.804
ABSOLUTELY.

17:53.273 --> 17:54.774
WHERE IS HE?

17:54.807 --> 17:58.778
I SENT HIM AWAY BECAUSE
I KNEW YOU WOULDN'T UNDERSTAND,
NO MATTER WHAT I SAID.

17:58.811 --> 18:00.447
NO, YOU SENT
YOUR--[INDISTINCT] AWAY.

18:00.480 --> 18:02.182
THAT'S RIGHT.

18:04.517 --> 18:06.219
NO!

18:06.253 --> 18:08.054
YOU GONNA HIT ME, MACK?

18:08.087 --> 18:10.623
YOU GONNA HIT ME?
IS THAT ALL YOU KNOW
HOW TO DO?

18:10.657 --> 18:13.726
YOU CAN'T CHARM IT,
YOU KILL IT!

18:13.760 --> 18:14.761
UGH!

18:14.794 --> 18:15.962
TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED!

18:15.995 --> 18:19.366
TELL ME THE TRUTH!

18:21.968 --> 18:23.270
GET OUT OF MY WAY.

18:23.303 --> 18:26.673
I'M MORE FAMILIAR WITH A GUN
THAN I AM WITH YOUR BODY.

18:26.706 --> 18:28.074
I WILL SHOOT YOU.

18:28.107 --> 18:32.212
I WILL GIVE YOU ONE SECOND
TO PUT THAT DOWN BEFORE
I TAKE IT FROM YOU.

18:33.112 --> 18:36.383
HA HA, YOU'RE
THE BIG MAN NOW.

18:36.983 --> 18:37.950
I'M LEAVING.

18:37.984 --> 18:39.952
YOU ARE NOT LEAVING!
WE'RE GONNA WORK THIS OUT.

18:39.986 --> 18:41.154
AND I'LL TELL ANYONE
WHO WILL LISTEN

18:41.188 --> 18:42.255
WHY MY HUSBAND'S
A PROUD SOLDIER

18:42.289 --> 18:45.192
BUT HE'S A POOR
EXCUSE FOR A MAN!
HE BEATS HIS WIFE!

18:45.225 --> 18:47.360
PEOPLE KNOW ME, TIFFY,
NO ONE'S GOING TO BELIEVE YOU.

18:47.394 --> 18:49.162
YOU'RE A HISTORY MAN
WHO KILLS FOR A LIVING.

18:49.196 --> 18:53.032
A MAN WHO STRUCK
HIS WIFE EVERYONE KNOWS
A FEW YEARS BACK--

18:53.065 --> 18:55.635
YOU TELL PEOPLE
WHATEVER YOU WANT.

18:55.668 --> 18:58.538
YOU EXPLAIN THIS.

18:58.571 --> 19:00.707
UGH! WHAT DID YOU DO?!

19:00.740 --> 19:01.674
OH!

19:01.708 --> 19:04.211
NO, LEAVE ME ALONE!
LEAVE ME ALONE!

19:04.244 --> 19:07.180
OUT OF MY WAY!

19:15.355 --> 19:18.124
WHERE DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE GOING?

19:18.157 --> 19:20.026
THIS IS MY UNIT.

19:20.059 --> 19:22.128
GOTTA GET SOMETHING
OUT OF MY LOCKER.

19:22.161 --> 19:23.796
PLACE IS OFF LIMITS,
BUDDY.

19:23.830 --> 19:25.465
COME ON, GUYS.
ONLY TAKE A MINUTE.

19:25.498 --> 19:26.533
YOU CAN COME WITH ME.

19:26.566 --> 19:28.968
AIN'T GONNA HAPPEN, PARTNER.
WE GOT ORDERS.

19:29.001 --> 19:29.736
COME ON.

19:29.769 --> 19:31.404
GIVE A SOLDIER A BREAK,
WILL YOU?

19:31.438 --> 19:33.039
IT'S JUST US.

19:33.072 --> 19:34.173
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT,
PARTNER.

19:34.207 --> 19:35.908
I'LL CALL A PATROL CAR,
TAKE YOU BACK
TO THE BARRACKS.

19:35.942 --> 19:38.478
YOU DON'T NEED
TO BE DRIVIN'
AFTER DRINKIN' A FEW.

19:38.511 --> 19:39.679
I COULD DO THAT FOR YOU.

19:39.712 --> 19:41.414
COME ON, MAN.

19:41.448 --> 19:43.082
OK, JACK, YOU HAD
YOUR CHANCE.

19:43.115 --> 19:46.052
AND SO DID YOU.

19:46.886 --> 19:48.755
POST ONE NEEDS ASSISTANCE.

19:48.788 --> 19:50.923
YOU BETTER
CALL 'EM ALL.

20:02.269 --> 20:03.536
COME ON, COME ON,
COME ON.

20:03.570 --> 20:06.273
WE DON'T WANT TO MAKE
A CAREER OF THIS.

21:11.137 --> 21:13.873
[FOOTSTEPS]

21:45.304 --> 21:48.174
[FOOTSTEPS]

22:17.036 --> 22:18.471
NO NUMBERS.

22:18.505 --> 22:20.840
THAT'S NO HELP.

22:38.124 --> 22:39.358
[SIGHS]

22:39.392 --> 22:41.193
HOW 'BOUT THAT?

22:41.227 --> 22:43.696
GOD HELP US ALL.

23:07.153 --> 23:08.455
WHAT'D YOU FIND OUT?

23:08.488 --> 23:12.258
I FOUND OUT THIS MAY GO BACK
TO SOMETHING THAT HAPPENED
IN PORTUGAL.

23:12.291 --> 23:14.427
SOME MISSION IN PORTUGAL.

23:14.461 --> 23:16.763
MY FRIEND OF A FRIEND
AT THE SENATOR'S OFFICE--

23:16.796 --> 23:18.831
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

23:20.299 --> 23:25.872
THOMAS R. RYAN,
P.O. BOX 372,
TIPPIT, TENNESSEE?

23:25.905 --> 23:28.708
HALLANDALE, FLORIDA.

23:28.741 --> 23:30.276
SWITZERLAND.

23:30.309 --> 23:32.344
GREECE.

23:34.180 --> 23:35.582
THESE ARE
EYES-ONLY ORDERS.

23:35.615 --> 23:38.284
WHY HAVEN'T YOU
HANDED THESE OVER?

23:39.318 --> 23:41.821
YOU'RE NOT
COOPERATING WITH THEM.
WHY AREN'T YOU COOPERATING?

23:41.854 --> 23:45.958
BECAUSE THEY'RE ABOUT
TO SEND MY MEN TO PRISON
FOR SERVING THEIR COUNTRY.

23:45.992 --> 23:47.393
YOU HAVE A FEDERAL SUBPOENA
TO HAND OVER--

23:47.426 --> 23:48.427
THAT'S IMMATERIAL.

23:48.461 --> 23:50.997
YOU'D BREAK A FEDERAL LAW?
THAT'S RIGHT.

23:51.030 --> 23:52.164
FOR YOUR CREW?

23:52.198 --> 23:53.500
THAT'S RIGHT.

23:53.533 --> 23:56.102
AND WHAT ABOUT OUR LIFE?

23:56.803 --> 23:57.737
COLIN SELVIN--
WHO IS HE?

23:57.770 --> 23:59.438
HE'S MY FRIEND
AT THE SENATOR'S OFFICE.

23:59.472 --> 24:01.608
COLIN SELVIN,
ALL RIGHT.

24:01.641 --> 24:03.175
HE SAYS YOU CAN
SAVE YOURSELF
IF YOU JUST--

24:03.209 --> 24:04.477
I WON'T
BETRAY MY MEN.

24:04.511 --> 24:05.745
BUT YOU WILL GIVE UP
ALL OF THE YEARS

24:05.778 --> 24:06.813
YOU SPENT GETTING
TO WHERE YOU ARE.

24:06.846 --> 24:09.949
TOM, YOU CAN END UP
PROSECUTED WITH YOUR MEN,

24:09.982 --> 24:11.684
PERHAPS JAILED,
HUMILIATED,

24:11.718 --> 24:14.020
DISHONORABLY DISCHARGED,
CAN'T GET A JOB.

24:14.053 --> 24:16.455
"WHAT HAVE YOU BEEN DOING
FOR THE PAST 20 YEARS?"

24:16.489 --> 24:17.524
"OH, I CAN'T TELL YOU."

24:17.557 --> 24:18.658
YOU THINK
I DON'T KNOW THAT?

24:18.691 --> 24:21.093
OR, YOU CAN COOPERATE
WITH WHOMEVER
THEY DIRECT YOU TO

24:21.127 --> 24:22.995
IN WHATEVER WAY
THEY ASK YOU TO,
UNDER THE LAW,

24:23.029 --> 24:26.132
AND THEN YOU ARE
IN A POSITION
TO HELP YOUR MEN,

24:26.165 --> 24:27.033
LEGALLY AND CORRECTLY.

24:27.066 --> 24:29.468
AND WHAT IF LEGALLY
WON'T WORK?

24:29.502 --> 24:30.469
THEN...

24:30.503 --> 24:33.540
I WON'T GIVE UP MY MEN.

24:34.373 --> 24:36.609
MY FAULT.
I DID THIS TO MYSELF.

24:36.643 --> 24:38.310
I WAS SO MAD, I JUST--

24:38.344 --> 24:39.278
STOP PROTECTING HIM.

24:39.311 --> 24:40.880
I SAID I DID THIS
TO MYSELF.

24:40.913 --> 24:43.015
YOU CUT YOURSELF?
THAT'S RIGHT.

24:43.049 --> 24:46.285
WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON
IN THIS PLACE?

24:46.318 --> 24:48.120
YOU SEE THIS?

24:48.154 --> 24:50.657
WHAT IS HAPPENING
TO ALL OF US?

24:50.690 --> 24:52.224
LEAVE HIM!

24:52.258 --> 24:53.292
MAYBE SHE SHOULD.

24:53.325 --> 24:56.395
BUT WHAT
DO YOU ADVISE
SHE DO AFTERWARD?

24:56.428 --> 24:57.697
LEAVE HIM NOW.

24:57.730 --> 24:59.966
AND GET AS FAR AWAY
FROM THIS PLACE

24:59.999 --> 25:01.133
AS HUMANLY POSSIBLE.

25:01.167 --> 25:04.537
EASY FOR YOU TO TELL
TIFFY TO JUST TOSS
AWAY HER HUSBAND.

25:04.571 --> 25:06.305
MAYBE SHE WON'T HAVE TO.

25:06.338 --> 25:09.341
ARMY LOOKS LIKE
IT'S GONNA DO IT
FOR HER.

25:09.375 --> 25:12.545
AIN'T THAT RIGHT?

25:15.782 --> 25:17.917
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

25:17.950 --> 25:19.619
ENTER.

25:25.424 --> 25:27.694
COLONEL RYAN REPORTING
AS ORDERED.

25:27.727 --> 25:31.430
COLONEL RYAN,
I'VE ASKED COLONEL BAZEMORE
TO BE HERE AS A WITNESS.

25:31.463 --> 25:32.531
YES, SIR.

25:32.565 --> 25:35.401
ALLEGATIONS
OF SEVERE MISCONDUCT,
CRIMINAL CONDUCT,

25:35.434 --> 25:37.369
HAVE BEEN BROUGHT AGAINST
MEMBERS OF THIS COMMAND.

25:37.403 --> 25:40.873
AND EITHER YOU KNEW
OF THESE ACTIVITIES
AND LOOKED THE OTHER WAY,

25:40.907 --> 25:41.874
OR YOU DIDN'T KNOW.

25:41.908 --> 25:44.176
EITHER WHICH IS CULPABLE
IN A COMMANDER.

25:44.210 --> 25:45.511
SIR, MAY I SPEAK?

25:45.544 --> 25:46.512
GO AHEAD.

25:46.545 --> 25:48.715
WHAT ARE THE CHARGES?
CLASSIFIED.

25:48.748 --> 25:50.082
SIR, 30 DAYS,
WHATEVER THE CHARGES,

25:50.116 --> 25:52.418
SHARE THEM WITH ME
SUFFICIENTLY TO ALLOW ME
TO REFUTE THEM.

25:52.451 --> 25:55.855
GIVE ME JUST 30 DAYS,
AND I WILL DO SO
TO YOUR SATISFACTION.

25:55.888 --> 26:00.593
THE FIRST DUTY
OF A COMMANDER
IS TO COMMAND.

26:00.627 --> 26:02.194
COLONEL RYAN, IT IS
MY CONSIDERED BELIEF

26:02.228 --> 26:04.096
THAT YOU HAVE FAILED
IN THAT PRIMARY DUTY.

26:04.130 --> 26:07.934
SIR, THIS UNIT
IS THE PRINCIPLE WEAPON
IN THE TERROR FIGHT,

26:07.967 --> 26:12.071
A UNIT WHICH TAKES YEARS
TO PREPARE, TRAIN AND FIELD.

26:12.104 --> 26:13.640
IF YOU WANT
TO BENCH ME, FINE.

26:13.673 --> 26:14.774
BUT IF YOU TAKE THOSE MEN
OUT OF THE FIGHT,

26:14.807 --> 26:16.108
YOU'LL BE HANDING
A VICTORY TO OUR ENEMIES.

26:16.142 --> 26:21.113
IT WOULD BE A MISTAKE
OF THE GREATEST CONSEQUENCE
TO THIS NATION.

26:21.147 --> 26:25.384
THAT'S A DECISION
THAT'S BEEN MADE
IN ANOTHER PLACE.

26:25.417 --> 26:27.486
COLONEL RYAN, I DO,
AS OF THIS INSTANT,

26:27.519 --> 26:29.656
RELIEVE YOU
OF THE COMMAND
OF THIS ORGANIZATION.

26:29.689 --> 26:34.460
YOU WILL CONSIDER YOURSELF
CONFINED TO QUARTERS
AND UNDER ARREST.

26:34.493 --> 26:36.629
THAT'S ALL.

26:45.137 --> 26:47.674
[SIGHS]

26:49.141 --> 26:50.943
[LAUGHTER]

26:50.977 --> 26:53.512
[DOOR OPENS]

26:57.884 --> 27:00.853
THE LEAGUE IS READY
TO HELP ANY OF YOU
WHO NEED IT.

27:00.887 --> 27:02.588
WE'RE STILL MISSING
A COUPLE OF BOYS
FROM ROLL CALL, RON.

27:02.621 --> 27:05.624
WELL, THE DESK SERGEANT
SAID THEY'RE GOING
TO HOLD MR. WILLIAMS

27:05.658 --> 27:07.259
TILL RYAN COMES
TO SIGN FOR HIM.

27:07.293 --> 27:10.296
APPARENTLY, OLD HECTOR
DID A NUMBER ON A COUPLE
OF THOSE BOYS.

27:10.329 --> 27:12.464
MM-HMM,
PROVIDING COVER FOR
A FAILED MISSION.

27:12.498 --> 27:15.334
WHAT IF THEY HAUL HIM OFF
FOR INTERROGATION?

27:15.367 --> 27:17.636
NO. HE'S IN
THE DRUNK TANK.

27:17.670 --> 27:19.171
WHEN I WAS
AT THE STATION,

27:19.205 --> 27:21.540
I HEARD HIM
SINGING HYMNS
BACK THERE.

27:21.573 --> 27:23.375
AT LEAST WE KNOW
WHERE HE IS.

27:23.409 --> 27:25.845
IT'S GREY
I'M WORRIED ABOUT.

27:25.878 --> 27:27.146
STILL NO WORD FROM HIM?

27:27.179 --> 27:29.381
WHAT THE HELL
HAPPENED TO HIM?

27:29.415 --> 27:31.050
IF HE'S LAYIN' LOW...

27:31.083 --> 27:32.484
THERE'S A REASON FOR IT.

27:32.518 --> 27:33.619
AND IF HE'S BEEN GRABBED?

27:33.652 --> 27:34.721
THEN HE'LL BUY US
SOME TIME.

27:34.754 --> 27:37.023
IF HE'S FREE,
HE'LL LEAD THEM ON
A MERRY CHASE.

27:37.056 --> 27:38.490
EITHER-OR,
CLOCK IS RUNNIN' DOWN.

27:38.524 --> 27:42.394
RYAN'S SECRET DIARY
WASN'T IN THE SAFE,
SO WHERE IS IT?

27:42.428 --> 27:43.629
HE MUST HAVE MOVED IT.

27:43.662 --> 27:45.364
WHY?
HMM.

27:45.397 --> 27:47.633
NEEDS HIS OWN INSURANCE.

27:47.666 --> 27:49.035
AND NOW WHAT?

27:49.068 --> 27:50.169
WE HAVE TO DECIDE.

27:50.202 --> 27:51.838
DO WE GO, OR DO WE
STAY AND FIGHT?

27:51.871 --> 27:54.573
WHATEVER YOU CHOOSE,
WHICHEVER WAY YOU GO,

27:54.606 --> 27:56.709
THE PROTECTIVE LEAGUE
WILL HELP YOU.

27:56.743 --> 27:58.978
PAY FOR LAWYERS,
OR IF YOU GO UNDERGROUND,

27:59.011 --> 28:02.414
SUPPORT YOU
AND YOUR FAMILIES
WITH COVER AND CASH.

28:02.448 --> 28:04.416
THAT'S A ROTTEN OPTION
FOR DOING YOUR JOB.

28:04.450 --> 28:09.956
FEELING SORRY FOR OURSELVES
AIN'T GONNA MAKE THE DONUTS.

28:10.289 --> 28:12.591
DO WE GO?
DO WE STAY?

28:12.624 --> 28:15.094
EACH MAN HAS
TO DECIDE FOR HIMSELF.

28:15.127 --> 28:16.528
'CAUSE IF YOU GO
TO LEAVENWORTH,

28:16.562 --> 28:18.965
CAN'T NOBODY DO THE TIME
EXCEPT YOU.

28:20.432 --> 28:21.400
ALL RIGHT, BOYS.

28:21.433 --> 28:25.704
IF THIS IS GOOD-BYE,
IT'S BEEN A HELL
OF A RIDE.

28:26.072 --> 28:27.974
AND I THANK YOU.

28:30.409 --> 28:32.078
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

28:32.111 --> 28:34.113
Woman:
NUMBER 24.

28:34.146 --> 28:35.848
SERGEANT MAJOR.
YES.

28:35.882 --> 28:37.116
SORRY TO KEEP YOU
WAITING, SIR.

28:37.149 --> 28:38.084
THAT'S QUITE
ALL RIGHT.

28:38.117 --> 28:39.551
I'D LIKE TO
MAKE A CHANGE
IN MY PAY STATUS.

28:39.585 --> 28:43.089
I'D LIKE YOU
TO PLACE EVERYTHING
EXCEPT FOR $50 A MONTH

28:43.122 --> 28:45.491
INTO AN ALLOTMENT
FOR MY WIFE.

28:51.597 --> 28:53.132
SERGEANT MAJOR,
IT SAYS HERE

28:53.165 --> 28:55.734
THAT YOUR ACCOUNT'S
BEEN FROZEN.

28:55.768 --> 28:56.969
FROZEN?

28:57.003 --> 28:59.438
FLAGGED. THERE'S
AN ORDER PLACING A FLAG
ON YOUR ENTIRE UNIT.

28:59.471 --> 29:02.942
IT SAYS NO FAVORABLE
PERSONNEL ACTION
MAY BE UNDERTAKEN

29:02.975 --> 29:04.276
FOR ANY MEMBER
OF YOUR COMMAND.

29:04.310 --> 29:07.446
FLAGGED,
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

29:07.479 --> 29:11.150
I GOT MY KID
GOING TO COLLEGE.

29:12.618 --> 29:14.153
WHAT DO I DO NOW?

29:14.186 --> 29:16.088
LOOK, SERGEANT MAJOR,

29:16.122 --> 29:19.258
WHAT DOES "FAVORABLE
PERSONNEL ACTION"
MEAN, ANYWAY?

29:19.291 --> 29:21.293
IN MY BOOK, IT MEANS
GETTING PROMOTED,

29:21.327 --> 29:24.296
GOING TO AN ARMY SCHOOL,
P.C.S.ing,

29:24.330 --> 29:25.431
THINGS LIKE THAT.

29:25.464 --> 29:27.266
BUT MOVING
YOUR OWN MONEY AROUND?

29:27.299 --> 29:29.601
WHAT'S SO FAVORABLE
ABOUT THAT?

29:29.635 --> 29:32.438
LOOK, I DON'T WANT YOU
TO VIOLATE ANY--

29:33.139 --> 29:35.441
MOLLY BLANE...

29:36.275 --> 29:40.146
ADDRESS,
ACCOUNT NUMBER.

29:41.480 --> 29:44.350
IT'S DONE,
SERGEANT MAJOR.

29:44.383 --> 29:45.484
SERGEANT ROSAS,
THAT WAS--

29:45.517 --> 29:47.820
AS LONG A SOLDIER
STAYS ON DUTY STATUS,

29:47.854 --> 29:51.090
THE ARMY CAN'T TOUCH
AN ALLOTMENT,
FOR ANY REASON.

29:51.123 --> 29:55.561
YOUR WIFE WILL
RECEIVE YOUR PAY
NO MATTER WHAT.

29:56.829 --> 29:59.531
ONE OF THE RARE ONES,
SERGEANT ROSAS.

29:59.565 --> 30:00.933
HAVE A GREAT AFTERNOON.

30:00.967 --> 30:02.201
YOU, TOO.

30:02.234 --> 30:03.669
THANK YOU.

30:03.702 --> 30:05.671
NUMBER 25.

30:05.972 --> 30:07.273
YOU DIDN'T SEE TIFFY.

30:07.306 --> 30:10.342
WELL, I DIDN'T SEE
THE BUS THAT HIT US
COMING, EITHER.

30:10.376 --> 30:12.845
BUT TIFFY LEFT.
WITH THE KIDS.

30:12.879 --> 30:13.980
SHE'S GONE.

30:14.013 --> 30:15.114
NOW GREY'S MISSING, TOO?

30:15.147 --> 30:19.018
MACK'S OUT CHASING SHADOWS,
WHAT'S NEXT?

30:19.051 --> 30:21.620
[CHUCKLES]
DON'T TOUCH THAT DIAL.

30:21.653 --> 30:23.822
SO? WHAT DO WE DO?

30:23.856 --> 30:26.225
WHAT DO YOU
WANT TO DO?

30:26.258 --> 30:28.194
FEEL SAFE.

30:30.997 --> 30:31.730
WHAT?

30:31.763 --> 30:32.831
DON'T WE HAVE TO CONSIDER

30:32.865 --> 30:35.567
WHAT THE C.I.A.
IS OFFERING HERE?

30:35.601 --> 30:37.536
FOR THE KIDS' SAFETY?

30:37.569 --> 30:38.537
FOR US?

30:38.570 --> 30:42.308
LOOK, WE STAY,
THE PRESSURE'S
GONNA BE A BITCH,

30:42.341 --> 30:44.343
ALL RIGHT?
A LOT OF SCRUTINY.

30:44.376 --> 30:45.311
HEARINGS...

30:45.344 --> 30:47.813
IF THEY BRING CHARGES,
THAT COULD MEAN PRISON.

30:47.846 --> 30:50.682
IF WE STAY, THE UNIT
MIGHT NOT EVER BE RESTORED.

30:50.716 --> 30:51.583
WHAT HAPPENS--

30:51.617 --> 30:52.751
IF I DON'T GO TO PRISON,

30:52.784 --> 30:55.721
ANOTHER JOB HERE,
A POSTING SOMEWHERE ELSE...

30:55.754 --> 30:56.923
ANOTHER MOVE.

30:56.956 --> 30:58.224
IF WE GO
WITH THE C.I.A.,

30:58.257 --> 30:59.558
WE'RE GONNA BE
RELOCATED ANYWAY.

30:59.591 --> 31:01.093
C.I.A.'S HOLDING OUT
A HAND.

31:01.127 --> 31:03.095
WHAT ARE THEY OFFERING?

31:03.129 --> 31:05.097
SAFETY.

31:06.465 --> 31:08.100
ARE THEY?

31:08.134 --> 31:09.068
[SIGHS]

31:09.101 --> 31:12.404
WELL, IT SURE AS HELL
DOESN'T FEEL SAFE HERE.

31:12.438 --> 31:14.941
[SIGHS]

31:17.743 --> 31:19.378
ALL RIGHT.

31:19.411 --> 31:21.647
I'LL PUT TEDDY TO BED.

31:22.114 --> 31:26.052
OK, BIG BOY.
I GOT YOU.

31:35.227 --> 31:38.297
Man: SERGEANT GERHARDT.

31:43.402 --> 31:45.938
AND YOU ARE TO BE HELD
IN PRE-TRIAL CONFINEMENT

31:45.972 --> 31:48.107
IN THE POST STOCKADE
UNTIL SUCH TIME

31:48.140 --> 31:49.375
AS YOU STAND
GENERAL COURT MARSHALL

31:49.408 --> 31:52.979
FOR CHARGES BROUGHT
AGAINST YOU AND YOUR TEAM.

31:53.312 --> 31:54.981
BUT I COULD BE CONVINCED
TO MITIGATE

31:55.014 --> 31:56.748
THE CIRCUMSTANCES
OF YOUR CONFINEMENT

31:56.782 --> 31:58.985
UNDER CONDITION YOU TELL ME
THE WHEREABOUTS

31:59.018 --> 32:03.255
OF SERGEANT MAJOR BLANE
AND SERGEANT GREY.

32:04.190 --> 32:05.624
HAVE YOU NOTHING TO SAY?

32:05.657 --> 32:07.059
NO, SIR.

32:07.093 --> 32:08.995
THEN YOU ARE DISMISSED.

32:10.462 --> 32:12.264
GERHARDT.

32:12.298 --> 32:15.101
DO YOU NO LONGER
SALUTE YOUR SUPERIORS?

32:15.134 --> 32:15.934
I SURELY DO.

32:15.968 --> 32:20.106
BUT IN THIS ROOM,
I HAVE NO SUPERIORS.

32:20.772 --> 32:22.341
AND YOUR TEAMMATES
BLANE AND GRAY,

32:22.374 --> 32:25.311
YOU CAN CERTAINLY IMPROVE
YOUR OWN POSITION, SERGEANT.

32:25.344 --> 32:26.612
JUST TELL ME
WHERE THEY CAN BE FOUND.

32:26.645 --> 32:28.780
I'VE BEEN WONDERING THAT
MYSELF, COLONEL.

32:28.814 --> 32:31.383
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE
WITH THEM?

32:33.152 --> 32:34.753
STAND AT EASE, SERGEANT.

32:34.786 --> 32:38.757
DUE TO A FORTUITOUS
MECHANISM THAT I'M NOT
SURE THAT I UNDERSTAND,

32:38.790 --> 32:40.592
YOU'VE BEEN AFFORDED
THE POSSIBILITY

32:40.626 --> 32:42.761
OF ESCAPING THE FATE
OF YOUR COMRADES.

32:42.794 --> 32:45.964
YOU'VE BEEN GIVEN
A CHOICE.

32:45.998 --> 32:48.467
DO YOU WISH TO TELL ME
YOUR DECISION?

32:48.900 --> 32:50.336
SIR, I'D LIKE
SOME MORE TIME--

32:50.369 --> 32:54.740
YOUR DECISION, SERGEANT,
BEFORE WE LEAVE THIS ROOM.

32:55.007 --> 32:56.542
SIR, I CAN ASSURE YOU,

32:56.575 --> 32:58.510
WITH THE UTMOST SINCERITY,

32:58.544 --> 33:00.679
THAT I DO NOT WISH
TO GO TO PRISON.

33:00.712 --> 33:03.615
DID YOU GIVE THEM
WHAT THEY WANTED?

33:03.649 --> 33:06.152
[SIGHS]

33:07.686 --> 33:10.189
NO.

33:10.922 --> 33:13.459
I DIDN'T GIVE UP
EVERYTHING I HAD
IN WASHINGTON

33:13.492 --> 33:15.561
TO WATCH SOME GENERAL
STEP ALL OVER YOU.

33:15.594 --> 33:18.064
AND I DIDN'T WORK MY ASS OFF
ALL THESE YEARS,

33:18.097 --> 33:20.232
HAND ON MY HEART,
DOIN' THE RIGHT THING,

33:20.266 --> 33:23.469
JUST TO LET ANYONE
MAKE ME A TRAITOR
TO MY MEN.

33:23.502 --> 33:25.171
[ICE CLINKING]

33:25.204 --> 33:28.574
ALL YOU GOT, CHARLOTTE...

33:29.541 --> 33:31.410
ALL YOU GOT,

33:31.443 --> 33:34.913
AT THE END OF THE DAY
IN THIS ARMY...

33:36.182 --> 33:38.417
IS YOUR WORD.

33:38.684 --> 33:41.753
SO YOU AREN'T GONNA FIGHT
FOR YOUR CAREER?

33:41.787 --> 33:43.822
NO.

33:43.855 --> 33:47.259
YOU ALSO HAVE
A MARRIAGE.

33:47.293 --> 33:49.895
THAT'S RIGHT.

33:50.529 --> 33:52.364
I'M ASKING YOU,
AS YOUR WIFE,

33:52.398 --> 33:57.035
SIMPLY TO OBEY THE LAW
AND TO OBEY YOUR SUPERIORS.

33:57.069 --> 33:59.605
I CAN'T DO THAT.

34:02.141 --> 34:03.442
IF YOU CAN'T FIGHT
FOR YOUR CAREER,

34:03.475 --> 34:06.145
THEN WHY SHOULD I FIGHT
FOR OUR MARRIAGE?

34:12.050 --> 34:14.220
[DIALING]
HANG UP THAT PHONE.

34:14.253 --> 34:16.255
I WILL NOT.
I WILL MAKE THIS CALL,

34:16.288 --> 34:18.457
AND I WILL PUT OUT
THE FIRE.

34:19.158 --> 34:23.495
I DID WHAT I NEEDED TO DO,
AND IT COST ME MY JOB.

34:23.795 --> 34:26.832
AND IT COST YOU
YOUR WIFE.

34:44.583 --> 34:47.119
JONAS?

34:47.153 --> 34:49.621
JONAS!

34:51.757 --> 34:54.793
[TELEPHONE RINGS]

34:55.327 --> 34:57.429
[RING]

34:57.463 --> 35:00.098
Charlotte: YOU'VE REACHED
TOM AND CHARLOTTE RYAN.

35:00.132 --> 35:01.400
PLEASE LEAVE A MESSAGE.

35:01.433 --> 35:03.135
[BEEP]
TOM, THIS IS MOLLY.

35:03.169 --> 35:04.903
THERE'S BLOOD ON THE...

35:04.936 --> 35:07.005
I CAN'T FIND...

35:07.038 --> 35:11.177
JONAS IS MISSING--
TAKEN!

35:11.477 --> 35:13.845
WHERE THE HELL
IS MY HUSBAND?

35:27.893 --> 35:30.629
[CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING]

35:41.740 --> 35:44.276
THIS?
THIS ISN'T OVER.

35:44.310 --> 35:45.511
IT'S OVER FOR YOU.

35:45.544 --> 35:47.279
NOW YOU LEAVE
THIS WOMAN ALONE.

35:47.313 --> 35:49.948
YOU GOT ANYTHING ELSE
TO TAKE UP WITH HER,
YOU GO THROUGH ME.

35:49.981 --> 35:51.317
I'LL GO
WHERE I NEED TO,
WHEN I NEED TO,

35:51.350 --> 35:52.384
AND I DON'T
BELIEVE THERE'S

35:52.418 --> 35:56.222
ANYTHING THAT SAYS
I GOTTA CONSULT
WITH YOU FIRST.

35:56.822 --> 35:58.890
IT'S A NEW RULE.

35:58.924 --> 36:01.360
IT'S A RULE I JUST MADE.

36:04.029 --> 36:07.333
I'LL GET SOME PEOPLE IN HERE
TO HELP YOU CLEAN THIS UP.

36:07.366 --> 36:11.537
FORGET ABOUT THE MAIDS.
WHERE'S MY HUSBAND?

36:12.204 --> 36:13.339
MOLLY...

36:13.372 --> 36:17.075
ONE GOOD THING
ABOUT DISAPPEARING
AS OPPOSED TO BEING AWOL

36:17.108 --> 36:18.877
IS THEY CAN'T BRING CHARGES.

36:18.910 --> 36:20.912
MISSING IS STILL
A DUTY STATUS.

36:20.946 --> 36:25.417
UNTIL THEY FIND OUT
WHO TOOK HIM,
JONAS' PAY CONTINUES.

36:25.451 --> 36:27.953
THEY CAN'T CHARGE HIM
IN ABSENTIA.

36:31.290 --> 36:34.226
I'M SO SORRY
FOR YOUR TROUBLE.

37:10.629 --> 37:13.299
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

37:46.465 --> 37:49.200
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

38:05.617 --> 38:07.319
BUENAS TARDES, SENOR.

38:07.353 --> 38:09.187
BUENAS TARDES, SENORA.

38:09.220 --> 38:11.890
[SPEAKING SPANISH]

38:14.460 --> 38:17.563
[JONAS SPEAKING SPANISH]

38:37.816 --> 38:40.619
MUCHAS GRACIAS.

38:40.652 --> 38:42.821
DE NADA, PAPACITO.

39:05.444 --> 39:08.013
[GRUNTING]

39:15.621 --> 39:17.322
NOW JONAS IS GONE.

39:17.355 --> 39:20.125
MAYBE KILLED.

39:21.092 --> 39:22.494
WHAT ARE WE STILL
DOING HERE?

39:22.528 --> 39:25.731
NOW, LOOK WE DON'T KNOW
FOR SURE WHAT HAPPENED
TO JONAS.

39:25.764 --> 39:28.667
YOU'VE BEEN WITH
THE UNIT 2 YEARS.

39:28.700 --> 39:29.901
YOU GONNA LET YOURSELF
BE PUNISHED

39:29.935 --> 39:32.003
FOR SOMETHING
THE UNIT DID
BEFORE YOU SIGNED ON?

39:32.037 --> 39:35.273
WELL, IT HAPPENED A MONTH AGO,
IT HAPPENED 5 YEARS AGO.

39:35.306 --> 39:37.242
YOU SIGN ON TO THE UNIT,
YOU'RE THE UNIT.

39:37.275 --> 39:40.479
YOU PICKED IT UP,
YOU CARRY IT.

39:42.948 --> 39:44.450
IT'S A HIGH PRICE
TO PAY

39:44.483 --> 39:45.617
FOR SOMEBODY ELSE'S
CRIMES.

39:45.651 --> 39:47.686
LOOK, SOMEBODY IN
SOME CONFERENCE ROOM
CALLS IT A CRIME,

39:47.719 --> 39:49.955
DOESN'T MAKE IT A CRIME.

39:52.090 --> 39:54.426
I CAN'T BETRAY MY FRIENDS.

39:54.960 --> 39:57.162
I CAN'T.

39:57.563 --> 39:59.465
WHAT WOULD THAT TEACH
OUR CHILDREN?

39:59.498 --> 40:03.435
YOU KNOW A BETTER QUESTION,
TELL IT TO ME.

40:05.170 --> 40:07.673
[SIGHS]

40:08.774 --> 40:11.477
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

40:19.017 --> 40:21.286
GRACIAS.

40:21.687 --> 40:23.489
GRACIAS, MARISOL.

40:23.522 --> 40:26.257
[SPEAKING SPANISH]

40:28.594 --> 40:30.228
OLD FRIEND.

40:30.261 --> 40:31.129
DOYLE.

40:31.162 --> 40:33.431
THE ARMY'S LOOKING
FOR YOUR KIDNAPPERS.

40:33.465 --> 40:36.768
THEY'RE ALREADY ACCUSING
THE C.I.A. FOR
YOUR DISAPPEARANCE.

40:36.802 --> 40:39.771
THE C.I.A. SAYS THE ARMY
HAS HIDDEN YOU.

40:39.805 --> 40:41.940
TELL THE OTHERS
IN THE LEAGUE
I APPRECIATE THEIR HELP.

40:41.973 --> 40:44.109
WELL, HERE'S WHO YOU ARE.

40:44.142 --> 40:45.811
ALCIBIADES McDONALD,

40:45.844 --> 40:48.914
PANAMANIAN
OF WEST-INDIAN DESCENT.

40:48.947 --> 40:50.849
HMM. MOTHER, FATHER,

40:50.882 --> 40:52.017
FAMILY?

40:52.050 --> 40:53.519
BROTHER IN PRISON,
OVER IN TRINIDAD,

40:53.552 --> 40:54.986
GONNA BE THERE
A COUPLE MORE DECADES.

40:55.020 --> 40:57.455
NO WIFE, NO OTHER
SURVIVING FAMILY.

40:57.489 --> 40:58.924
AND THE REAL ALCIBIADES?

40:58.957 --> 41:00.592
WHAT'S HE UP TO
THESE DAYS?

41:00.626 --> 41:02.127
WENT MISSING
A FEW YEARS AGO.

41:02.160 --> 41:04.696
ANYBODY KNOW
WHAT HAPPENED TO HIM?

41:04.730 --> 41:07.733
ONLY ME.

41:08.867 --> 41:11.136
YOU'LL PICK UP
WHERE THE BROTHER
LEFT OFF--

41:11.169 --> 41:13.304
TRADER ALONG
THE CARIBBEAN COAST.

41:13.338 --> 41:17.042
FROM COLON
TO BOCAS DEL TORO.

41:17.075 --> 41:19.010
HUH. WHERE AM I
BASED OUT OF?

41:19.044 --> 41:20.712
VILLAGE OF BELÃ‰M.
IT'S REMOTE,

41:20.746 --> 41:24.750
BUT THE ALCALDE THERE
HELPS ME IN
SOME OTHER MATTERS.

41:30.589 --> 41:31.456
MY BOAT?

41:31.489 --> 41:33.324
YEAH, IT'S WAITING FOR YOU
IN PORTO BELLO.

41:33.358 --> 41:35.493
COUPLE OF RELIABLE BOYS,
MY BOYS,

41:35.527 --> 41:38.964
ONBOARD AS FIRST MATE
AND DECKHAND.

41:38.997 --> 41:41.066
CERTIFICATE
OF INCORPORATION,

41:41.099 --> 41:42.133
BANK ACCOUNTS...

41:42.167 --> 41:44.335
THE LEAGUE PAID
THE INITIAL SET-UP
COSTS FOR THIS,

41:44.369 --> 41:46.371
BUT IT'S
A REAL BUSINESS, JONAS.

41:46.404 --> 41:49.374
WE EXPECT IT
TO MAKE A PROFIT.

41:49.407 --> 41:50.909
COMMUNICATIONS PLANS?

41:50.942 --> 41:54.179
SINGLE-SIDEBAND RADIO
IN THE BOAT,

41:54.212 --> 41:55.313
ONE-TIME PADS.

41:55.346 --> 41:56.548
NEVER USE THE PHONE
FOR CONTACT.

41:56.582 --> 41:58.817
THE GRINGOS LISTEN
TO EVERYTHING IN PANAMA.

41:58.850 --> 42:00.686
IF IT'S ROUTINE, USE
ONE OF THE DEAD DROPS.

42:00.719 --> 42:03.088
IF IT'S PRESSING,
SEND ONE OF THE BOYS.

42:03.121 --> 42:05.356
IF IT'S AN EMERGENCY...

42:05.390 --> 42:08.860
POINT THE BOAT TOWARDS
BRAZIL AND GET UNDERWAY.

42:08.894 --> 42:10.228
COVER YOUR NAKEDNESS.

42:10.261 --> 42:12.197
[GUN CLICKS]

42:12.230 --> 42:14.900
MUCH APPRECIATED.

42:22.941 --> 42:24.009
AND JONAS--

42:24.042 --> 42:25.343
YEAH?

42:25.376 --> 42:27.879
IF THEY FIND YOU,
THEY'LL KILL YOU.

42:27.913 --> 42:31.316
THAT AIN'T EXACTLY NEWS.

43:03.815 --> 43:05.150
DONE.

43:05.183 --> 43:08.987
NOW THAT IT'S DONE,
WHEN CAN I GET MY WIFE
AND MY CHILDREN OFF BASE?

43:09.520 --> 43:10.822
WHY THE SAD FACE?

43:10.856 --> 43:12.057
IT AIN'T
ONE OF MY BETTER DAYS.

43:12.090 --> 43:16.561
WELL, SMILE, SOLDIER,
'CAUSE YOU AIN'T
A SOLDIER ANYMORE.

43:16.594 --> 43:17.562
YOU'RE IN
THE MAJORS NOW.

43:17.595 --> 43:18.463
LOOK, WHEN CAN
MY FAMILY LEAVE

43:18.496 --> 43:21.299
AND WHERE ARE
WE BEING SENT?
[DOOR OPENS]

43:22.600 --> 43:26.838
YOU WANT TO KNOW THE COLOR
OF YOUR NEW KITCHEN, TOO?

43:28.640 --> 43:29.307
I SHOULD'VE KNOWN.

43:29.340 --> 43:32.678
YOU'D THINK SO,
WOULDN'T YOU?

43:33.812 --> 43:34.780
MR. BROWN,

43:34.813 --> 43:36.247
YOUR FIRST ASSIGNMENT.

43:36.281 --> 43:38.116
NO, FIRST, MY FAMILY
NEEDS TO GET SETTLED.

43:38.149 --> 43:41.319
WE GET RELOCATED,
YOU GET MY DAUGHTER
INTO A NEW SCHOOL,

43:41.352 --> 43:42.688
YOU GET MY WIFE
A JOB AND THEN--

43:42.721 --> 43:44.122
YOU'RE ON THE CLOCK
NOW, MR. BROWN.

43:44.155 --> 43:47.425
YOU'RE ON THE INSIDE,
AND YOUR TROUBLES ARE OURS.

43:47.458 --> 43:49.928
YOU GIVE MY MAN A LIST
OF YOUR REQUIREMENTS

43:49.961 --> 43:51.262
AND WATCH THEM PERFORMED.

43:51.296 --> 43:52.597
WHAT DO YOU WANT FROM ME?

43:52.630 --> 43:54.966
WE'VE MISPLACED SOMEONE.

43:55.000 --> 43:56.702
WE WANT YOU
TO FIND HIM ASAP.

43:56.735 --> 43:57.602
GET SOMEONE ELSE.

43:57.635 --> 43:59.004
NO, THIS ONE'S
PERFECT FOR YOU.

43:59.037 --> 44:01.707
WE NEED YOU
AND YOU'RE GOING OUT.

44:01.740 --> 44:03.775
FIND THE MAN.

44:03.809 --> 44:08.013
ALL RIGHT, GIVE ME
THE BACKGROUND INFO.
WHAT'S HIS NAME?

44:10.515 --> 44:12.217
JONAS BLANE.

44:18.189 --> 44:19.958
Bob: AND WHAT IF
I CAN'T FIND HIM?

44:19.991 --> 44:21.727
Kern: THEN IT'S OFF
TO PRISON WITH YOUR MATES.
